openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: "1.0"
  title: Local Stub
  description: API of the local stub for local Kubernetes emulation
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:9000
paths:
  /api/agencies:
    get:
      description: returns basic information about all agencies
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK - agency information
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/StubAgencyConfig'
    post:
      description: create a new agency
      requestBody:
        description: configuration of new agency
        content:
          applications/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/StubAgencyConfig'
        required: true
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Created
components:
  schemas:
    StubAgencyConfig:
      description: configuration of agency container
      properties:
          masid:
            description: ID of MAS for pod name
            type: integer
          agencyid:
            description: unique ID of agency
            type: integer
          imid:
            description: unique ID of image group
            type: integer
          image:
            description: name of docker image
            type: string
          logger:
            description: switch for logging module
            type: boolean
          mqtt:
            description: switch for MQTT module
            type: boolean
          df:
            description: switch for DF module
            type: boolean

Error: notImplemented: path "/api/agencies": post: requestBody: contents: unsupported content types: [applications/json]
